{"tid":1090672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶吵架 玩命女瞓彌敦道馬路","createTime":"2019-04-03T15:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T16:01:53.000Z","uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4f7334e7da537632fff680fa7b25a84f5b2dd2","tid":1090672,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"住在油麻地的讀者Jolly，周三清晨6時正於睡夢之中，突然聽到街外傳來一男一女爭執聲，好奇往下望，驚見一名女子竟躺卧於中南廣場對開的彌敦道中線上，完全不動，由於女子右手張開，右腳折曲，與意外現場極為相似，但旁邊有一名男子背對女子走遠，其間有巴士在旁經過。女子見男子不為所動，自行站起來邊高聲喝罵邊向男子步近，「打我吖！我行埋嚟畀你打！」由於Jolly沒有全程觀看，不清楚男女最終結局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVrUzyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVrUzyS.png&h=7d7c40db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bb886359b32ca9ed55dfb7206d2cc1193d6545b","tid":1090672,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"車撚死佢就岩正傻閪"},{"pid":"2959419da18da0e06c0f056c516208472a2e709f","tid":1090672,"uid":99930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T15:34:22.000Z","msg":"風吹得路好長 一顆心晃呀晃<br />\n多想找人陪我逛 累了睡在馬路上<br />\n表面上很倔強 其實內心一團糟<br />\n怕自己愛像太陽"},{"pid":"4bfe58311119c036bfa938ce3169d5d2af4d998e","tid":1090672,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T15:42:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0626c1205a7249f2133c13cfd876a344c25979b3","tid":1090672,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"唔係咁開心呀"},{"pid":"af9ba85c7cad20fbe273de0d7630c701fa69b087","tid":1090672,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T15:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ByjrqNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FByjrqNx.jpg&h=dc4d22a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ea849ff46081e4dd79a7f797fc3b41140b1bef9","tid":1090672,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2959419da18da0e06c0f056c516208472a2e709f","tid":1090672,"uid